OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772568683
OL,3,CRelieved British Gulf tourists return
OL,4,Chome with tales of explosions and
OL,5,Csirens
OL,7,FTourists returning from Dubai say they
OL,8,Fare 'relieved' to be back in the UK
OL,9,Fafter fighting began in the Middle
OL,10,FEast over the weekend
OL,12,FBritish tourists returning from Dubai
OL,13,Fhave spoken of being on "tenterhooks"
OL,14,Fwhile missiles exploded and alarm
OL,15,Falerts sounded after fighting began in
OL,16,Fthe Middle East over the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
