PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772568683
OL,3,CRelieved British Gulf tourists return
OL,4,Chome with tales of explosions and
OL,5,Csirens
OL,7,FSome passengers arriving at Manchester
OL,8,FAirport on Tuesday 3 July, told ITV
OL,9,FNews they were "tearful" after
OL,10,Freporting "bombs dropping" around
OL,11,Ftheir hotels.
OL,13,FThey've described the "frightening"
OL,14,Fordeal of hearing and seeing missiles
OL,15,Fraining down as alerts went off on
OL,16,Ftheir phones.
OL,18,FOne passenger became tearful as she
OL,19,Fdescribed what she saw. She said: "I
OL,20,Fwas staying in the Westin overlooking
OL,21,Fthe marina...they were just...scary."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772568683
OL,3,CRelieved British Gulf tourists return
OL,4,Chome with tales of explosions and
OL,5,Csirens
OL,7,FAnother said: "At every point, when
OL,8,Fwe're boarding or landing, you're just
OL,9,Fexpecting something to happen, that
OL,10,Fyou don't want to happen."
OL,12,FOne woman at the arrivals gates said
OL,13,Fshe was grateful to her airline. She
OL,14,Fsaid: "We were very, very lucky with
OL,15,FEmirates, they put us into a safe
OL,16,Fhotel outside the area.
OL,18,F"There were bombs dropping around
OL,19,Fus...it wasn't great...I'm still
OL,20,Ftearful."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
