OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772568683
OL,3,CRelieved British Gulf tourists return
OL,4,Chome with tales of explosions and
OL,5,Csirens
OL,7,FSince the latest conflict between Iran
OL,8,Fand the US and its allies began on
OL,9,FSaturday, there have been widespread
OL,10,Fairspace closures in the Middle East,
OL,11,Fsparking major disruption to flights.
OL,13,FRoughly half a million passengers use
OL,14,Fairports in Dubai, Doha or Abu Dhabi a
OL,15,Fday, which are vital hubs for travel
OL,16,Fbetween Europe, Asia and Australia.
OL,18,FIt is expected to take several days to
OL,19,Fclear the backlog of passengers
OL,20,Fwaiting to travel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
